---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import InfoPages from "../layouts/InfoPages.astro";
import AmandaImg from "../assets/images/team/amanda.jpg";
import DiegoImg from "../assets/images/team/diego.jpeg";
import MichelleImg from "../assets/images/team/michelle.png";
---

<InfoPages title="Biographies">
  <div class="container content">
    <h1>Biographies</h1>

    <div class="row mt-5">
      <div class="col-12">
        <Image
          src={AmandaImg}
          alt="Amanda Smith"
          style="width: 120px; height: 120px; object-position: top; object-fit: cover;"
          format="webp"
        />
        <h2 class="mt-3">Amanda Smith</h2>
        <p class="fw-bold">Director of Event Sales</p>

        <p>
          Amanda has more than 15 years working in the event industry and
          planned many fun events like our New Year's Eve party when she ran a
          catering company of her own. You're in great hands.
        </p>
        <hr />
      </div>
      <div class="col-12">
        <Image
          src={DiegoImg}
          alt="Diego Von Schmeling"
          width={120}
          height={120}
          format="webp"
        />
        <h2 class="mt-3">Diego Von Schmeling</h2>
        <p class="fw-bold">Manager</p>

        <p>
          Diego has been with Rosie's for more than 14 years and runs a tight
          ship. Previously he owned his own caf√© and restaurant among other
          things. He will be your first contact when you arrive on New Year's
          Eve.
        </p>
        <hr />
      </div>
      <div class="col-12">
        <Image
          src={MichelleImg}
          alt="Michelle Tanhoff"
          width={120}
          height={120}
          format="webp"
        />
        <h2 class="mt-3">Michelle Tanhoff</h2>
        <p class="fw-bold">Manager</p>

        <p>
          Michelle is the newest addition to Rosie's but has worked for many New
          York institutions including the Metropolitan Opera, R Bar, among
          others. You will see Michelle everywhere at the party.
        </p>
        <hr />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</InfoPages>

<style>
  .content {
    margin-top: 5rem;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
</style>
